Compressed Mean [Alibaba SQL Interview Question]

Question:-

You're trying to find the mean number of items per order on Alibaba, 
rounded to 1 decimal place using tables which includes information on 
the count of items in each order (item_count table) and the corresponding 
number of orders for each item count (order_occurrences table).

Code:-

SELECT ROUND(
              SUM(item_count::DECIMAL * order_occurrences) /
              SUM(order_occurrences),2) AS mean
FROM items_per_order;
